title: Dean Chance, 1964 Cy Young Award winner and former Cleveland Indian, dies at age 74
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Indians - Today 
Dean Chance, who won the 1964 Cy Young Award and later pitched a no-hitter, died Sunday. He was 74....
